dets and the Institute Opportunities for fellowship  mentoring and networking among VMI graduates Small group sessions led by VMI graduates with ministry experience in missions  evangelism  church planting  military chaplaincy and discipleship  Mark your calendar and plan to be part of this significant ministry event  Hotel group rates available at  Holiday Inn Express Lexington  540 463 7351 Best Western Plus Inn at Hunt Ridge  540 464 1500  More lodging information CH  Maj  John Casper  04   casperjp vmi edu Mrs  Patricia Mountain   mountainpm vmi edu Related Information Chaplain s Office Chaplain James Park Assoc  Chaplain John Casper  04   50th Anniversary of Ministry to the Corps Mary Cannon Secretary to the Chaplain Old Hospital Virginia Military Institute Lexington  VA  24450 P   540  464 7390 F   540  464 7727 VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu skip to content VMI VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI Menu About About Us Administrative Offices Institute Report News  Photos  Videos VMI Archives Museums VMI Museum System The VMI Museum New Market Battlefield Stonewall Jackson House For Visitors Directions   Map Employment Parents   Family Conferences Chessie Nature Trail Bookstore Resources MyVMI Directories Friendly URLs Post View Health and Safety Computing Academics Areas of Study Majors   Minors Arts   Humanities Engineering Information   Social Sciences Life Sciences Natural S