vent  Hotel group rates available at  Holiday Inn Express Lexington  540 463 7351 Best Western Plus Inn at Hunt Ridge  540 464 1500  More lodging information CH  Maj  John Casper  04   casperjp vmi edu Mrs  Patricia Mountain   mountainpm vmi edu Related Information Chaplain s Office Chaplain James Park Assoc  Chaplain John Casper  04   50th Anniversary of Ministry to the Corps Mary Cannon Secretary to the Chaplain Old Hospital Virginia Military Institute Lexington  VA  24450 P   540  464 7390 F   540  464 7727 Commandant s Office Clubs and Events Health  Welfare  and Safety Regimental Band About Cadet Leadership Student Consumer Information Parents and Family Info Cadet Sign In   Out Cadet in Barracks   Cadet out of Barracks   Holly Leech  Commandant Office Manager P   540  464 7313 F 540  464 7748 E  leechhc vmi edu   OC  540 464 7293  OB 135  Evening Night OC 540 464 7962  OB 123  or 540 464 7285   NB 496  Guard Room  540 464 7294  Jackson Arch  Commandant s Office Virginia Military Institute Jackson Arch  Barracks Lexington  VA 24450  Commandant s Office Clubs and Events Health  Welfare  and Safety Regimental Band About Cadet Leadership Student Consumer Information Parents and Family Info Cadet Sign In   Out Cadet in Barracks   Cadet out of Barracks   Holly Leech  Commandant Office Manager P   540  464 7313 F 540  464 7748 E  leechhc vmi edu   OC  540 464 7293  OB 135  Evening Night OC 540 464 7962  OB 123  or 540 464 7285   NB 496  Guard Room  540 464 7294  Jackson Arch  Commandant s Office Virginia Military Institute Jackson Arch  Barracks Lexington  VA 24450 Commandant s Office Clubs and Events Health  Welfare  and Safety Regimental Band About Cadet Leadership Student Consumer Information Parents and Family Info Commandant s Office Commandant s Office Clubs and Events Clubs and Events Health  Welfare  and Safety Health  Welfare  and Safety Regimental Band Regimental Band About Cadet Leadership About Cadet Leadership Student Consumer Information Student Consume